task.summary: Default task

Finalized and perfected the drawing of GUI viewer by reversing both pitch labels and inverted the y coordinated of corresponding beat boxes (green and black). Also refined the loops drawing column and row grid lines to draw to the end of the last measure that the last beat was in. This was accomplished by implementing -- private int completeMeasure() that returned how many more beats are needed to make the number of beats cleanly divisible by 4, in other words, making the x2 coordinate (endpoint x coordinate) always is a multiple of four, ensuring that the piece does not cut off mid measure.
